A Full Cover for "Perfect" - Ed Sheeran
.
.
Finally got around to recording this song. I've been pretty preoccupied with classes lately, so it was nice to get out and get this one done. 
I also wasn't expecting to record the entire song, but you know, I was enjoying that nice 60 degree February weather. Its by no means "perfect" ðŸ˜‰, but considering it was a four minute take with my phone, I'm more than happy with it.
.
